arStrings.szText: I'm telling you the truth. I saw my neighbor reading a book about forbidden Horadric magics. He wants to sow chaos!
Insistent (but in reality the villager is probably lying about his neighbor because of some personal vendetta)
(sigh) Right, right. This wouldn't have anything to do with the money you owe him, would it?
Going through the motions--not convinced that this villager is telling the truth, but trying to stay civil
